description: Gushen, Inc., through its subsidiaries, provides educational services. The company offers onsite educational services, including individual development, youth leadership, and development programs. It also operates Wisdom Lighthouse, an application for online family educational services that provide parents a convenient platform to access courses. In addition, the company offers education consulting services; sell and rent books; organize book clubs; and sells educational electronic devices. Further, it engages in the consultancy and information technology support; and promotion and support services. Gushen, Inc. was incorporated in 2015 and is headquartered in Beijing, China.
